title: ASTA Global Convention Ends on a Decided High Note
text:
Last updated: 04:15 PM ET, Thu September 03 2015 ASTA Global Convention Ends on a Decided High Note Travel Agent | American Society of Travel Agents (ASTA) | Claudette Covey | September 03, 2015 
Photo by James Shillinglaw 
ASTA’s Global Convention ended on a decided high note, with the society’s officials noting that attendance easily doubled that of last year’s conference aboard Norwegian Cruise Line’s Breakaway.
